data.description: No SHOWINGS BEFORE 12:00 ON SATURDAY!! Beautifully updated 3-bed 2 bath 4-sided brick ranch a stone's throw from Canton Street and the Chattahoochee River.  Charming entryway welcomes you into the cozy family room with brick fireplace.  Completely open to the stunning new kitchen featuring stainless appliances, eat-in breakfast area and walk-in pantry with barn door.  Formal dining room with wall of windows.  Additional room could be office or workout room.  Oversized primary bedroom with large walk-in closet.  Gorgeous primary bath with lovely tile & glass shower and stand-alone tub.  No carpet in the house.  Huge corner lot with fenced backyard.  Roof 6 years old. Deep into the community.  Very quiet.  Located in the award-winning Roswell HS school district.  Swim/tennis neighborhood.  HOA optional.
